SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 19 O.S. 2021, Section 165, as last
13
14
amended by Section 1, Chapter 229, O.S.L. 2024 (19 O.S. Supp. 2025,
14
15
Section 165), is amended to read as follows:
15
16
Section 165. A. In lieu of reimbursement for traveling
16
17
expenses within their county, each county commissioner and sheriff
17
18
may shall receive a monthly travel allowance of up to One Thousand
18
19
Dollars ($1,000.00). In lieu of the reimbursement for traveling
19
20
expenses authorized by law for each county officer, each county
20
21
assessor may shall receive a monthly travel allowance of up to Nine
21
22
Hundred Dollars ($900.00), and each county clerk, court clerk, and
22
23
county treasurer may shall receive a monthly travel allowance of up
23
24
to Eight Hundred Dollars ($800.00). Each such county officer may
